description: Depicts a loving couple consisting of a person with a medium-dark skin tone and a man, united by a heart. This emoji conveys themes of love, commitment, and affection within a romantic relationship.
apple_vendor_description: This Apple emoji depicts a loving couple with distinct medium-dark and dark skin tones, their connection emphasized by a vibrant red heart floating between them. Rendered with Apple's characteristic soft rounded edges and realistic lighting, the heart appears luminous and full of affection. On Apple devices, this visual storytelling conveys deep romantic love, partnership, and a strong bond between two women, embodying warmth and intimacy.
